      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IRON LADY (5) was quickly into stride and burnt early from the middle draw where she gave a sight, finishing second (22.84) and beaten 2.75 lengths over 400m at this track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can find winning form. ZIPPER TRAIN (1) turned in a better effort at Gosford last start, finishing third behind Golden Status (22.69) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from four starts. Expecting another good run. FROGGY DID IT (2) is a solid beginner and with a good start can clear the draw. Last start finished last over 400m at this track beaten 9 lengths (23.01) behind Road To Fame in a Grade 5 on March 16. Looks suited here and can measure up. VALKYRIE HEAT (7) cannot be ruled out.",
